"Latent factor variances and their moderation effects. Estimates are on the "
"log scale internally and back-transformed for display. Significant "
"moderation indicates that the spread of the latent trait changes across the "
"moderator."
msgstr ""

msgid "Factor Means"
msgstr "Médias dos Fatores"

