msgstr "VIF não pôde ser calculado."

msgid "Endogenous Indicator Prediction"
msgstr "Previsão de Indicadores Endógenos"

msgid ""
"Cross-validated prediction of endogenous indicators using PLSpredict. The "
"prediction metrics assess how well the PLS-SEM model predicts indicator "
"scores out of sample."
msgstr ""

msgid "Prediction Metrics"
msgstr "Métricas de Previsão"

msgid ""
"MAE (mean absolute error), RMSE (root mean squared error), and Q² prediction "
"metrics for endogenous indicators. Q² > 0 indicates that prediction error is "
"less than using the training sample mean. When benchmarks are included, "
"lower MAE/RMSE than the benchmark suggests the PLS-SEM model predicts better."
msgstr ""

