"Estimated covariances between latent variables (~~ operator). These "
"represent undirected associations between latent variables."
msgstr ""

msgid "Variables"
msgstr "Variáveis"

msgid ""
"Residual variances of the observed variables: the variance not explained by "
"the latent variables. Negative residual variances (Heywood cases) may "
"indicate model misspecification."
